casebody.head_matter:
Sean M. DONAHUE, Petitioner,
v.
Eugene SCALIA, Secretary of Labor, et al.
No. 19-7573.
Supreme Court of the United States.
April 6, 2020
Motion of petitioner for leave to proceed in forma pauperis denied, and the petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Third Circuit dismissed. See Rule 39.8.
